name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Every bit counts - to say thanks we’ll make sure you're the first to get Membus updates during the grand tour, and throughout our preparations.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Your name will be hand-inscribed on the Membus itself. Historians of the future will gape in awe as they read your name and contemplate the incredible leap forward in language learning that you made possible.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Choose a country and receive a postcard from the tour, written by a member of the crew or a sweet stranger. One thing is sure, it will inspire you to learn the language!

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: We will provide guidelines for you to film yourself saying your favourite swear-word in any language. Be creative, more originality means more chance to be the only one teaching the word. + one month subscription to Memrise Pro in January 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Film yourself telling your favourite joke in your native language, and we'll feature it in a special collection in the app. A unique opportunity to showcase the unique humour of your country. + one month subscription to Memrise Pro in January 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - The ultimate status symbols of the accomplished language learner will be yours: a Memrise notebook and a sticker pack delivered to your door! + get your new year's learning off to a flying start with a one month subscription to Memrise Pro in January 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: All the content on Memrise is of course free to learn, and videos will be free for everyone to learn from. But there are extra learn modes, stats and other brain boosting add-ons that only the Memrise Pro learner can access. With this truly astonishing kickstarter-exclusive lifetime deal, you could become a Pro learner - for just *half* the price of an annual subscription (£40). Snap this one up because it won't hang around long!

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - A beautiful Memrise cotton 'tote' bag and a sticker set delivered to your door. Its stylish, practical, environmentally friendly, and clearly demonstrates your support for the greatest language learning adventure in history. What more could you ask of a humble bag? + one month subscription to Memrise Pro in January 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - Give us a phrase or word that will be filmed in all languages during the tour. Would it be "I'm flabbergasted"? "Spoons are awesome"? or "Are you having a laugh?"? Nothing is too absurd to film, so let your creative juices flow! + a one month subscription to Memrise Pro in January 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - A Limited edition Memrise T-shirt and a sought-after sticker pack, delivered to your door. You should know: this will be quite the hottest fashion item of 2016. + one month subscription to Memrise Pro in January 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Today and today only, we have a special deal for Memrise lovers. Get a yearly subscription to Memrise Pro for the year of 2016 at half price, and a Memrise notebook and stickers delivered to your door. The perfect bundle for the language nerd. And cheap on top of that!

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: If you missed the £20 ones (where they were practically given away), you have now the opportunity to get a lifetime Pro Membership for our regular yearly price! Jump in quick before these are all snapped up too!

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - The Memrise T-shirt, Memrise notebook and  Memrise sticker pack, all impeccably wrapped up in the Memrise tote bag. + one month subscription to Memrise Pro in January 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: It is widely agreed that one of the most effective ways to learn a language is to find yourself a lover who speaks that language. With this garment of incomparable style and beauty you will find yourself drawing in lovers like moths to a flame. For those who don't know, a dressing gown is a "long, loose robe, typically worn after getting out of bed or bathing". + Memrise Pro membership for the full year of 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: We have a special group deal for three days only: Four Yearly Memrise Pro Memberships for the price of two! Treat your family, friends, chess club or water polo team this Christmas with this brainy gift which you will enjoy all year long.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: If you want to help us achieve our goal and get this Kickstarter exclusive deal at the same time, grab the opportunity before it vanishes, very possibly forever!

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - Earn for yourself the immense privilege of being one of the people to teach the phrase "I love you" to millions of learners of your languages all over the world. You will become one of the faces of this phrase which will bring you untold fame and glory. (We'll provide you guidelines to film yourself, allowing you to master the art of video selfie. A versatile life skill) + Memrise Pro membership for the full year of 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - You'll become one of the friendliest and fondest memories of millions of language-learners when you bid them welcome into the official Memrise course for your language. + A Memrise Pro membership for the full year of 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - If that is true or not doesn't really matter. What matters is that you will be the person teaching this phrase to millions of learners of your native language! When they will think of someone awesome, your face will definitely be the one that pops to their mind. + A Memrise Pro membership for the full year of 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: These lifetime subscriptions are in demand, so we're releasing another batch of one hundred. This reward is a Kickstarter exclusive so grab this deal now!

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - Simple but impactful, you'll be the first person anyone sees when they start learning the language. They will remember your face with great nostalgia and gratitude when attaining fluency (We’ll provide guidelines for filming yourself) + Memrise Pro membership for the full year of 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: - In true moments of conviviality, you must know how to toast (people, not bread). From "Prost!" to "Skål!" to "Salud", say it like you mean it and teach it to thousands of language learners (We’ll provide guidelines for filming yourself) + Memrise Pro membership for the full year of 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Our portrait-artist-in-residence will skilfully render 30 lucky faces on the Membus. Just send us a photo of yourself for the artist to work from, and you'll travel around Europe with the bus, surveying her beautiful landmarks. + A Memrise Pro membership for the full year of 2016

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Help us refurbish our bus! You will be the proud owner of one of our seven beds and have a golden plaque with your name on it. You can also add a message or bio if you wish to fully express yourself.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: *The travel to and from the Membus won't be paid for but everything else will. Sometime between May and July 2016, depending on the country you want to road-trip through.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: We'll host you and your friends one private party in each of France, Germany, Spain, Italy and Portugal. The Membus will descend on the town, village, hamlet, school or retirement home of your choice. We'll film you, your buddies, your colleagues, lovers and whomever else you desire. As the daylight fades we will invite you aboard the Membus as our resident barman mixes sun-downer cocktails and the music begins to play. These are widely expected to be some of the most seminal European parties of 2016. Sometime between May - July 2016, depending on the country.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: More extravagant and deluxe than the beds, this is an opportunity to shine by sponsoring our Royal Suite. Made with great taste, people will fight to get the privilege to spend the night in this luxurious enclosure. You will of course also have a say in the decoration of the suite.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Call the Membus to your school or university, anywhere in the UK for a half day event. We have a team of linguists, neuroscientists, memory experts and event organisers. Together we will throw you a language-learning festival at a school / university / prison or any other institution of your choice. And we'll film your students, putting them into the first ever video dictionary of English! The exact event plan will be finalised in discussion with you. It will happen in April 2016.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: The ultimate team summer holiday - you and your friend for a week on the Membus in a country of your choice. There's nothing in life quite like friendship, and the greatest way to celebrate life with friends this summer will surely be on the Membus! Share the most luxurious quarters of the Membus with your besties, while zooming across Europe in a true carnival of language, travel and fun. *The travel to and from the Membus won't be paid for but everything else will. Sometime between May and July 2016, depending on the country you want to road-trip through.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Pick a language, any language, and we will provide you with the ultimate immersive learning experience here in London. You will have a personal language coach and special activities tailored to the language of your choice. The rest of the time you will be able to enjoy the charms of Albion and we will throw you a party at our glorious headquarters.

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Become a celebrated Kickstarter sponsor. You will be known forever as one of the four trusty wheels that drove the Membus forward, set its course and carried the full weight of all our hopes and dreams on your broad rubber shoulders. The newspapers of Europe will ring with reports of your generosity and vision !

name: Membus Tour: creating the world's first video dictionary
reward_description: Tell us a language that you would like to see made with videos. We will parachute a team to record them and you will be able to choose part of this course's phrases. It will happen in 2016 in discussion with you.

Mach deine eigene iPhone App. (Xcode 7, iOS 9 und Swift 2)
reward_description: Mit dieser Option sage ich zum einen Danke und weiter so, zum anderen möchte ich unbedingt etwas dazu beitragen, dass es bald neues, frisches VideoMaterial gibt. Dabei werde ich mit Vornamen und dem ersten Buchstaben des Nachnamens gefolgt von einem Punkt als Unterstützer im Abspann jedes der Trainingsvideos aus dieser Kickstarter-Campagne gelistet. Das komplette Abspann-Video werde ich im August als Download-Link erhalten :-) Wenn das Projekt hier auf Kickstarter zustande kommt, erhalte ich im Juli 2015 per Email eine ordentliche Rechnung über den gezahlten Betrag.

name: Mach deine eigene iPhone App. (Xcode 7, iOS 9 und Swift 2)
reward_description: Dabei wird mein voller Name im Abspann der Trainingsvideos aus dieser Kickstarter-Campagne als Mäzen genannt und ich erhalte im August 2015 einen MemoryStick mit dem Abspann per Post. Wenn das Projekt hier auf Kickstarter zustande kommt, erhalte ich im Juli 2015 per Email eine ordentliche Rechnung über den gezahlten Betrag.

name: Mach deine eigene iPhone App. (Xcode 7, iOS 9 und Swift 2)
reward_description: Ich will nur die Videos :-) Ich kann nicht viele Abende live dabei sein. Ich will einfach nur alle Videos und Beispielprojekte zum Downloaden, und zwar genau dann, wenn alles fertig ist, also ab dem 10. August 2015. Keine Fragen an den Dozenten, kein Einzelcoaching, keine Hausaufgaben, kein Abschlusstest. Genau so soll es für mich sein :-) Die einzelnen Themen der 25 Veranstaltungen habe ich der Beschreibung entnommen und ich weiss, dass ich 75 Stunden VideoMaterial zur Ausbildung zum iOS-App-Entwickler zum Download erhalten werde. Wenn das Projekt hier auf Kickstarter zustande kommt, erhalte ich im Juli 2015 per Email eine ordentliche Rechnung über den gezahlten Betrag.

name: Mach deine eigene iPhone App. (Xcode 7, iOS 9 und Swift 2)
reward_description: Als Kickstarter unterstütze ich die Erstellung des 75-Stunden VideoTrainingsProgramm für die Ausbildung zum iOS-App-Entwickler. Dabei möchte selbst live dabei sein und Stück für Stück miterleben, wie sich der Kurs zusammen baut. Ich möchte nicht bis August warten, um endlich als iOS-Entwickler tätig zu werden, sondern ab dem 06.07. das neu gelernte umsetzen und endlich meine eigene App realisieren :-) Ich will keine Hausaufgaben und keinen Abschlusstest. Fragen möchte ich auch keine stellen, vor Ort bei Franky muss ich nicht sein und Einzelcoaching brauche ich auch nicht. Ich möchte aber live an den Webinaren teilnehmen und gleich ab dem 06.07.2015 um 18:00 Uhr mit dabei sein. Alle Quelltexte und Beispielprojekte und natürlich alle Videos stehen mir nach der Seminarreihe als Download zur Verfügung. Vom 06.07.2015 bis zum 07.08.2015 bin ich Montags bis Freitags von 18:00 bis 21:00 Uhr als Webinar-Teilnehmer dabei, und arbeite mich intensiv in die Thematik der App-Erstellung für iPad, iPhone & Co. ein. Die ausführliche Beschreibung mit allen Daten, Terminen und Themen habe ich gelesen und freue mich schon auf die kommenden, spannenden Stunden :-) Wenn das Projekt hier auf Kickstarter zustande kommt, erhalte ich im Juli 2015 per Email eine ordentliche Rechnung über den gezahlten Betrag.

name: Mach deine eigene iPhone App. (Xcode 7, iOS 9 und Swift 2)
reward_description: Als Kickstarter unterstütze ich die Erstellung des 75-Stunden VideoTrainingsProgramm für die Ausbildung zum iOS-App-Entwickler. Dabei möchte für mich selbst das Maximum an Lernerfolg sichern und bin deshalb live als First-Class-Premium-Teilnehmer mit dabei. Hausaufgabenkontrolle, Abschlusstest, Einzelcoaching und vor Ort Termine inklusive :-) Vom 06.07.2015 bis zum 07.08.2015 bin ich Montags bis Freitags von 18:00 bis 21:00 Uhr dabei, und arbeite mich intensiv in die Thematik der App-Erstellung für iPad, iPhone & Co. ein. Die ausführliche Beschreibung mit allen Daten, Terminen und Themen habe ich gelesen und weiß, dass ich an bis zu sechs Abenden auch live bei Franky in Ober-Mörlen mit dabei sein kann :-) Alle Quelltexte und Beispielprojekte und natürlich alle Videos stehen mir nach der Veranstaltung als Download zur Verfügung. Ich weiß, dass es Hausaufgaben und einen Abschlusstest geben wird, das finde ich klasse, denn ich meine es jetzt richtig ernst mit meiner Ausbildung zum App Entwickler. Ok, ok, die Hausaufgaben sind freiwillig, der Abschlusstest bestimmt jedoch die Bewertung die ich auf meinem Teilnehmerzertifikat erhalten werde. Da freu ich mich jetzt schon drauf :-)) In der Zeit vom 06.07. bis zum 07.08. kann ich drei Coaching-Termine vereinbaren, um im Einzelgespräch mit Franky etwaige Verständnisfragen oder aktuelle App-Probleme zu klären. Jeder dieser Termine kann bis zu 30 Minuten dauern, wir sind dabei per Telefeon, Skype und/oder Teamviewer verbunden, so dass jeder seinen Bildschirm teilen kann um Problem und Lösung zu verdeutlichen. Wenn das Projekt hier auf Kickstarter zustande kommt, erhalte ich im Juli 2015 per Email eine ordentliche Rechnung über den gezahlten Betrag.

name: Jaspr - An app to bring cash-free trade to the digital world

name: Jaspr - An app to bring cash-free trade to the digital world

name: The First Laws of This Land - A Self Guided Walking Tour
reward_description: We are famous for our Sea of Hands installation that has been exhibited across the whole continent, from beaches on the West Coast to Parliament House in Canberra. Assistant Producers will get an official Sea of Hands pin for you to wear with pride.

name: The First Laws of This Land - A Self Guided Walking Tour
reward_description: We've been educating people about land justice, reconciliation and harmony for  over 20 years. Producers will receive a set of three our official Sea of HANDS pins to keep or share as gifts.

name: The First Laws of This Land - A Self Guided Walking Tour
reward_description: You may have seen one of the acknowledgement plaques we have produced in collaboration with First Peoples, they're famous!

name: The First Laws of This Land - A Self Guided Walking Tour
reward_description: If there's one thing we've done well over the last twenty years is collect a fantastic selection of books about activism, solidarity and history of First Peoples, so we know what's good. Assistant Directors will get one of our gorgeous coffee tables book called FIRE (RRP $50); which documents the use of fire by First Peoples as a land management tool.

name: The First Laws of This Land - A Self Guided Walking Tour
reward_description: Last Christmas we kicked off our Justice Reinvestment campaign.  This campaign was calling for governments to create a fairer and smarter justice system that instead of jailing people worked to divert them from crime through rehabilitation. Executive Producers will get to see what justice reinvestment and other legal issues look like 'on the ground'. Executive Producers will be given an exclusive tour through one of the court facilities that are designed to prevent re offending and divert perpetrators to support services instead of jails.

name: The First Laws of This Land - A Self Guided Walking Tour
reward_description: What does the RMIT Law School have in common with two tragic executions, the Queen Victoria Market car park, The Queen Mum, a police strike, a riot, Sir John Monash and the decapitated head of Ned Kelly?  If you become a star and go for a walk with us- we'll tell you.  Get in quick, spaces on this tour will be very limited.

name: The First Laws of This Land - A Self Guided Walking Tour
reward_description: Without our supporters we just simply would not exist, we love all of you and some of you have been with us since the very start. You too can play a big role in the life of ANTaR Victoria by becoming a patron. Patrons will get to leave the app at home because instead of having a self guided tour through the app you get to go for a historical walk around Melbourne with us! What does the RMIT Law School have in common with two tragic executions, the Queen Victoria Market car park, The Queen Mum, a police strike, a riot, Sir John Monash and the decapitated head of Ned Kelly?  If you become a Patron and go for a walk with us- we'll tell you. Patrons will receive a copy of the fantastic book Pandora's Box (RRP $150) that documents the history of Aboriginal Affairs in Australia. Today, little is known about the history of the development of Aboriginal Affairs. Pandora's Box, as the title suggests, blows this history open with an insider's account of the Council for Aboriginal Affairs.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This abstract color study, like many of these pieces, is a 1-off. This photograph does not quite capture how vibrant the colors are. In person, they are spectacular. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This piece is inspired by Salvador Dali’s timescapes. It is of a melting and angry head sculpture in a luscious landscape. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: Imagine that you are in a forest in a Dali dreamscape. This was my inspiration for this beautiful painting. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This painting was done using chiaroscuro and chalk pastel. The parts that were taken out back to white were then painted over using different colors. I love this piece. There is a certain energy to it, similar to Vincent Van Gogh's Wheatfield with Crows. It has the same amount of dark energy. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This is one of my favorites of the cross-hatched paintings I did. It was one of the first works I did on dark subject matters, which continues on today with my film work. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This two-colored silkscreen is part of a triptych of photographs from the back of the bus. Done in 3 silk screens of complementary colors, these pieces were inspired by my long trips to art school on the city bus each morning and night. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This was one of the first art pieces where I put my own socio-political beliefs into my creative work. It depicts a group of apparitions, possibly of citizens dead from the war, laughing at a platoon of soldiers below. It was meant to show the complete lack of importance of war on the human spirit. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This large silk screen was hand painted using a reductive method of a waterproof paint on a silk screen, which is then covered with fuddle emulsion and then erased with water. The painting represents global citizens all working together for a diverse world. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This painting was done during the period where I was doing many illustrations using watercolor combined with color pencil and ink. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This work, inspired by Pablo Picasso's Blue Period, is one of the rare pieces for which I affected the canvas itself to exemplify the content. Cut Up in Pieces was part of my early introspection as an artist and creator. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: Growing up, I had intense nightmares-- sometimes eight in one night. This painting was inspired by this. For many, it may evoke Terry Gilliam's dystopian cult film, Brazil. With its foreboding grayscale imagery, this eerie painting will shock all of your visitors and art lovers. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This large silkscreen was colored by hand to add more vibrancy to the original Out in the World. The painting shows global citizens all working together for a diverse world. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: I love this painting. It is one of my favorites of my charcoal on paper pieces. The painting was done under a self-imposed time constriction of 30 minutes. I consider it my most successful piece done with duration challenges. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This piece was inspired by science fiction pulp comics that I was reading at the time, as well as  the monthly releases of Juxtapoz comics. Like many of these paintings, it simultaneously brings me sadness and joy to sell it. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This large-format illustration was done using water color pencil. Because of this the colors are very bright and vivid. In person the painting is even more vibrant than it appears in this photograph. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This 1996 painting was part of a continued series of water color pencil, large-format illustrations that I completed over the next two years. The hours of work alone are what make this worth its price. Very vibrant and will liven up any space. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This painting was hanging in my bedroom for years. It is inspired by the comic book series "Infinity Gauntlet," a Marvel Comics miniseries I read when I was in my early teens. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This was my largest mosaic piece, and it took the longest to complete. Working on it three hours a day, I completed it over the course of more than a month. This was done in my high school in grade 12 after returning from my travels to India. It shows resilience in a time of self-reflection. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This painting was done soon after my travels to India in my last year of high school. Feeling a new sense of maturity, I came back feeling so much more empowered and worldly. The secret is the new things I learned but was unable to explain. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: The AXS Map Mapathon project
reward_description: This is a blowup that was inspired from watching images in my sketch books expanded to fullscreen in When I Walk. Limited edition print signed by Jason DaSilva.

name: Convers8 | The world can be lonely. You don't have to be.
reward_description: Get in the driver's seat and send three unique questions to all users in Convers8's newsfeed. In the newsfeed, users answer questions submitted exclusively by the founders everyday to identify common interests to create more interesting connections and see what's on everyone's mind. For your reward, you'll be allowed to post three of these questions - of your choosing - to the ENTIRE C8 community (in accordance with Convers8's requirements on content and language, of course). You'll also get EVERYTHING from the previous reward levels!

name: Convers8 | The world can be lonely. You don't have to be.
reward_description: For your kindness, you'll get a couple of items. First, you'll get a hand-painted (by the founder of your choice), personalized mug to show off to your friends and co-workers (and prove the founding team's undying love and appreciation for you). 'Is it also a great conversation starter?' you ask. You bet! You'll also get a special icon next to your username for the life of the app. Plus...you get EVERYTHING from the previous reward levels such as the Conversation Starter Kit, three posts into the C8 newsfeed, voting rights, and a 'Thank You' email from the team!

name: Convers8 | The world can be lonely. You don't have to be.
reward_description: At this tier, you'll decide what feature you'd like us to develop next. Unlike other tiers, though, you're not voting for a feature that we already proposed...you're choosing the feature yourself (as long as it conforms to the Convers8 terms and conditions and is aligned with the Convers8 mission). Basically, if it can be developed for $500, we'll build it. Don't worry though, because you're still getting the sweet personalized mug from the founders, the Conversation Starter Kit, 3 questions in the Newsfeed, and Thank You email.

name: Convers8 | The world can be lonely. You don't have to be.
reward_description: You decide what next-level features and capabilities we create. You tell us how to make people's lives better. To do this, we'll be in close coordination with you along the way to make sure we're building this feature to your specs, so get ready for some interesting conversations with the founders. And...obviously...you get EVERYTHING from the previous levels.

reward_description: Fitivity MVP – With “MVP” status, you will get exclusive access to the Fitivity Virtual Coaching app and get your first three months of training free. You also get access to all perks in Player and All Star status.

reward_description: Fitivity Hall of Fame – With “Hall of Fame” status, you will receive an exclusive team wristband and INSIDER updates on Fitivity’s progress, as well as a thank you letter signed by the executive team. In addition, we will create a training program in your name -- designed specifically for your needs. Lastly, we will allow you to submit a workout video that will forever be used in our apps, to be seen and performed by millions! Last but not least, we will give you early access to all future Fitivity apps and features. You will also get access to all perks in Player, All Star, and MVP status.

name: Fitivity - The Pickup Sports App That Will Actually Work
reward_description: Fitivity Legend – With “Legend” status, Fitivity will give your city or town priority to where we auto-create create pick-up games first. For some cities it can take a few weeks to do the research and add local athletic venues to our database --   and we can only do one town/city at a time. This perk is perfect for you if you would like us to prioritize your city or town first, so we can get your community active now!  You will also get access to all perks in Player, All Star, MVP, and Hall of Fame Status.

name: Fitivity - The Pickup Sports App That Will Actually Work
reward_description: Fitivity Super Legend – With “Super Legend” status, you will get early access to our Virtual Coaching app and get grandfathered in, to pay a consistent special $20/month flat monthly fee for life, to work with a top tier group trainer whom monthly training fee is $150/month! You will be getting $130 worth of free training from one of the top sports and fitness trainers for the rest of your life! You also get access to all perks in Player, All Star, MVP, Legend, and Hall of Fame Status.

name: Fitivity - The Pickup Sports App That Will Actually Work
reward_description: Fitivity Game Changer – With “Game Changer” status, we will give you super early access to your own password protected event management website, to create and participate in your own custom created local events that the app will promote to our users. reward_description: Ein riesen Dankeschön für die Spende. Du erhältst zusätzlich eine signierte INN-Sammlerpostkarte und hast die Möglichkeit, mit dieser bei unserem Social Network-Spiel teilzunehmen! ENGLISH INNcredible thanks for supporting our project! You will receive a cool signed postcard-collectible with which you will be able to take part in our social networking game!

name: INN App
reward_description: Bei einer 10 € Spende dürft Ihr Euch aus sagenhaften drei Belohnungen eine aussuchen! 1. Offiziell signiertes INN Merchandise Paket mit Postkarte, Poster und Stickern. Teilnahme am Social Network Gewinnspiel! 2. Egal ob um mit den Katzen zu spielen oder am nächsten Tag die Präsentation zu meistern, mit dem INN LASERPOINTER funktioniert alles. 3. Natürlich gibt es aus etwas für einen gesellschaftlichen Abend oder der langweiligen Zugfahrt mit Freunden: Das INN Kartenspiel vertreibt sämtliche Langeweile ENGLISH If you support us wiith 10€, you may choose from the following gifts: 1. The official INN Merchandise Pack, signed and containing a poster,stickers and the postcard from above. 2. Got a cat? Or an important presentation? The INN Laserpointer and Flashlight Set is going to help you while dangling from your keychain! 3. Poker? Black Jack? The INN deck of cards will eliminate any kind of boredom. Good luck!

name: INN App
reward_description: Wenn Ihr 15€ spendet, dürft Ihr euch unter folgenden Belohnungen entscheiden: 1. Die Occulus Rift ist Euch zu teuer, aber Ihr möchtet trotzdem in die virtuelle 3D Welt eintauchen und in New York am Times Square stehen und die Wolkenkratzer ansehen? Mit dem offiziellen INN Virtual 3D Projector, wandelt Ihr jedes Smartphone im handumdrehen in ein atemberaubendes 3D Erlebnis! Ob Spiele, Städte oder Filme, Ihr entscheidet wo Ihr hingeht! 2. Oder möchtet Ihr lieber einen Smartphone-Verstärker, mit dem Ihr den kompletten Raum beschallen könnt und einfach an Euren Schlüsselanhänger haften könnt? Ihr habt die Wahl! ENGLISH If you support us with 15€, you can choose between the following: 1. The Occulus Rift is too expensive, but you want to feel the virtual reality anyway? With the spectacular INN Virtual 3D projector you can turn any smartphone into a virtual 3D world. Games, cities or movies, you decide where you go with your friends and don´t forget to share! 2. Or do you prefer the smartphone amplifier for your keychain? Simply attach it to your phone and your music will be heard anywhere you go!

name: INN App
reward_description: Bei 20€ gibt es folgendes zur Auswahl: 1. Einen INN Hipster Jutebeutel oder Turnbeutel, zum Coolsein und Eure geliehenen Sachen zu transportieren! 2. Oder ein trendiges INN T-Shirt, um cool durch den Sommer zu kommen! ENGLISH 20€ will get you either: 1. The INN Hipster Clothbag. Cool and individual, exactly what you need to go shopping or carry your rented items around in. 2. Perhaps you´d prefer the offifial INN T-shirt to get through the hot summer? Cool design and cool colors will make you look INN.

name: INN App
reward_description: Bei 50€ erhältst du entweder: 1. Das offizielle INN Büro-Set: Eine INN Tasse, Kulli mit Notizblock und Merchandise. Pack(Poster,Postkarte,Sticker) 2. Wir senden Euch eine bereits halbvolle Einwegkamera mit lustigen Bildern von uns und unserem Leben und natürlich dem Projekt! Dazu gibt es natürlich noch das Merchandise Paket. (hier ist das internationale Porto etwas geringer) 3. Vielleicht werden Euch aber auch die INN Bluetooth Lautsprecher für Euer Smartphone begeistern? Hiermit könnt ihr einfach die Lautsprecher mit Eurem Telefon verbinden, oder nur als Radio nutzen! ENGLISH 50€, wow thanks so much! You may choose: 1. The official INN Office-Set offers everything you need for your office table: The INN Cup, a pen with a notepad and the merchandise pack! 2. We are going to send you a half filled One-Way Camera, showing you our lives and the progress of the project! Plus the merchandise pack! (International shipping is slightly less) 3.Or do you prefer the INN Bluetooth Speakers? Simply connect your smartphone via bluetooth and listen to high quality sound wherever you are. Can also be used as a radio!

name: INN App
reward_description: Bei 100€ bedanken wir uns zutiefst mit folgenden tollen Geschenken; entweder: ENGLISH Support us with 100€ and choose: 1. The INN Cooling&Grilling Combopack will aid you with any trip to the park or into nature. Simply stow what you want to take along into the Combopack and put on the grill once you get there. Save room and time! 2. Or if you feel adventurous, you might prefer the INN Adventure Set! Consisting of everything necessary for living off grid, this set even fits into your wallet! Cutting your steak has never been easier, off grid. Want to make a fire? Use the magnifying glass. Tweezers and a compass turn the set into everything you need!

name: INN App
reward_description: Für 250€ bedanken wir uns damit, dass wir dich als Co-Creator in unserem Legal Notice verewigen! Zusätzlich gibt es folgende Auswahl: 1. Du kannst entweder einen fashen Rucksack mit einer ausgezeichneten Auswahl der Geschenke oben haben! 2. Oder du entscheidest dich doch eher für den Rucksack, der ein atemberaubendes Picknick/Grillset mit Kühlbox beinhaltet. Klein und effektiv! ENGLISH If you support us with 250€, we will name you as a co-creator in our legal notice and give you a spectacular present: 1. You will receive an amazing backpack with individually chosen presents from the top. 2. Or we will fill the backpack with the incredible picnic-cooler-grill set which you can take anywhere due to its size! Share the moment with the ones yo love!

name: INN App
reward_description: Bei 500€ bist Du zu unserer offiziellen und exklusiven INN Release Party in Berlin eingeladen. Hier zeigen wir Dir die wichtigen (Underground-) Orte der Hauptstadt und nehmen Dich Abends zur offiziellen Release-Party mit! ENGLISH If you have just supported us with 500€, you are going to receive an INNvitation for our official INN Release Party in Berlin! We are going to give you a tour of the spectacular (underground) sites and take you along to the party in the evening!

name: INN App
reward_description: 1.000€ spendet nicht jeder. Hierfür möchten wir uns herzlich bedanken und zusätzlich eines der folgenden anbieten: 1. Beratung von Bernd Kunkel (8h Kommunikations- und Marketingberatung) 2. Individuelles Fotoshooting mit Anna Hermann, Porträt, Bewerbung, Image, o.Ä. (3h Shooting Plus 15 digitale Abzüge) 3. Ein Imagefilm im Stil des INN-Videos von Joshua Weigand-Suminski (max. 2 min) ENGLISH 1.000€ That is quite something. We would like to thank you for your trust an support and would like to offer the following: 1. Marketing and Communication Consulting by Bernd Kunkel (8 h) 2. Individual Photoshoot with Anna Hermann (3h plus 15 digital Prints) 3. Did you like our Fundingvideo? Also want one? Joshua Weigand-Suminski will make you one (max 2 min)

name: INN App
reward_description: Wer 1000€ oder mehr spenden möchte, tritt am besten persönlich mit uns in Kontakt. Am besten Du meldest dich bei jaws@i-need-now.com, dann erhältst du ein Infopaket samt den Konditionen. ENGLISH If you would like to support us with a large amount of money, please contact Joshua Weigand-Suminski via mail at jaws@i-need-now.com and you will receive an infopack with the conditions.

reward_description: Reward: App-Knowledgements! Have your always wanted your name in lights? Well, pixels are even better! Your name will be part of a special acknowledgements section in version 2.0 of Cosplace for iOS and Android.

name: Cosplace: A Photo App For Sharing Your Cosplay Life
reward_description: We took tons of awesome photos over the past 14 months of cosplayers from our growing community. We'll send you five in digital format, hand-picked by Cosplace's founder. They'll be super high-res so you can print them, or use them as wallpaper on your computer, or even an actual wall!

name: Cosplace: A Photo App For Sharing Your Cosplay Life
reward_description: We'll mail you one beautiful 5x7 or 7x5 postcard printed on premium glossy card stock. The front will feature one of five striking photos we captured of cosplayers in our growing community. The back will feature a thank you message, a personal anecdote about the photo, and the signature of our founder. Check out the rewards section to see some of the postcards. The rest are surprises :-) Add-on available: Want all five postcards? Add $15 to your pledge and you'll get the entire five card set. Previous reward levels included!

name: Cosplace: A Photo App For Sharing Your Cosplay Life
reward_description: Oh the joy of peeling and sticking. The sticker pack includes three 4x6 sticker sheets from featuring our collection of Cosplace "Con Buddies", original characters inspired by some of the most popular cosplays you've seen, plus our very own mascot, Conrad! As a bonus, you'll also get a 4-inch die cut logo for sticking to your laptop or anything else! All stickers are made by Stickermule and are made of a durable, high-quality, weather-resistant vinyl material. Want more than one sticker pack? Add additional packs to your pledge for only $15 each. Check out the rewards section to see the sticker designs! Shipping to U.S. is included! All previous reward levels are also included!

name: Cosplace: A Photo App For Sharing Your Cosplay Life
reward_description: This isn't your standard corporate swag. Our logo is the baddest in all of fandom, and you'll get a large one screen-printed on a premium t-shirt in Cosplace purple. Add additional t-shirts to your pledge for only $30 per shirt! Sizes available are YXS-3XL All previous reward levels are also included!

name: Cosplace: A Photo App For Sharing Your Cosplay Life
reward_description: When you're at a busy convention it can get frustrating when someone takes your picture without getting your contact info. We want to help with that! This reward includes 500 standard business card-sized calling cards. The front features the Cosplace logo and your app username. The back will be blank white for jotting down notes or other contact info that you can give to a photographer, fan, or anyone! You'll also get a digital PDF so you can re-order more cards anywhere business cards are sold. Once the next version of Cosplace is released, we'll send out surveys so you can give us your app username.

name: Cosplace: A Photo App For Sharing Your Cosplay Life
reward_description: This is our entry level in-app showcase rewards! You'll be part of a small group of users showcased over 100 days in Cosplace for iOS and Android. Your showcase will come via app alert that will appear in the notification stream of every single Cosplace user. When users touch the notification, it will take them to your Cosplace profile screen, so make sure you've got lots of great posts to show off for all those new followers. We have a limited quantity at this level, so act fast! Previous reward reward are also included! Shipping cost is for included physical rewards.

name: Cosplace: A Photo App For Sharing Your Cosplay Life
reward_description: What can we say about capes that hasn't been said by millions before? Capes are fun. Capes are rad. Capes! The official Cosplace cape was designed by a member of our community. It's made of a high quality performance spandex, and it comes in purple with a sewn white Cosplace logo on the back. They come in small or large. Unfortunately our capes do not harness any supernatural powers or abilities, but we've been wrong before. All previous reward levels are included!

name: Cosplace: A Photo App For Sharing Your Cosplay Life
reward_description: Of the photos we've taken in our short history, this one is without a doubt our favorite. It perfectly encompasses our belief that cosplay is where you make it. It comes comes printed on premium glossy poster stock, and is obviously suitable for framing and hanging in your man or lady cave. This reward includes a postcard-sized version that includes a note about the history behind the photo, with a signature from Cosplace's founder (who also took the photo!) All previous reward levels are also included!

reward_description: The Explore section of Cosplace will be the central hub for discovering amazing cosplay. Worbla Challenge will also be a featured category where you'll be able to share your project from start to finish. After all, there's nothing wrong with a little friendly competition. name: The Realize Legacy - The World's First Digital Heirloom
reward_description: Answer a few simple questions... From there, the software will generate three versions. You can pick one and customize from there or start off from scratch! Choose from a huge selection of meaningful images, fonts and colors. Then pick from a library of sayings, proverbs and quotes from some of the smartest minds and greatest poets to have ever walked the Earth: Einstein, Jefferson, Whitman to name only a few. Or put in your own family sayings! "Grandpa always said..." or "My Mom always told me..." It's totally customizable! The software is your cultural canvas - you are Picasso! Plus... "The Five Cultural Pillars of Perseverance" An EASY-to-read, five-page PDF. Five ideas to inspire perseverance in a growing mind.

name: The Realize Legacy - The World's First Digital Heirloom
reward_description: The goal is not to live forever. It's to create a Legacy that does. How It Works My team of graphic designers and artists create a meaningful image based on your color preferences, tastes and styles. You and I collaborate via email, phone and/or Skype (or in person if you live in the New Orleans area) to create a Legacy that embodies your cherished values and inspires generations of your family to become the best they can be. Want something traditional? Edgy and bold? Elegant and prestigious? Want to emphasize your Faith? Integrity? Perseverance? Creativity? It's up to you! Unlimited revisions. I'm not happy until you're proud to show it to your family. Digital copies delivered in multiple formats. Plus... Three uses of the Realize Legacy app (can be given as gifts). Plus... "The Five Cultural Pillars of Perseverance" An EASY-to-read, five-page PDF. Five ideas to inspire perseverance in a growing mind.

name: The Realize Legacy - The World's First Digital Heirloom
reward_description: The goal is not to live forever. It's to create a Legacy that does. Families have been commissioning heirlooms for thousands of years. Be among the first to commission the world's first digital heirloom with the Realize Legacy. How It Works I work with elite graphic designers and world-class artists to create a meaningful image based on your color preferences, tastes and style. Want something traditional? Edgy and bold? Elegant and prestigious? Want to emphasize your Faith? Integrity? Perseverance? Creativity? Perhaps you'd simply like to protect a growing mind from the pitfalls of privilege. Whichever ideas you want to accentuate, we'll construct a culture around them that's unique to you and your family, including (but not limited to)... We collaborate via email, phone and/or Skype (or in person if you live in the New Orleans area) to create a Legacy that embodies your cherished values and inspires generations of your family to become the best they can be. Unlimited revisions. I'm not happy until you're proud to show it to your family. Digital copies delivered in multiple formats and a matted and framed copy (customized by you) from our partners at framebridge.com or Pineapple Gallery in Covington, LA (for those of you in the New Orleans area). You are the steward of your Family Culture. I am Michelangelo, hammer and chisel in hand. Plus... Five uses of Realize Legacy app (can be given as gifts). Plus... "The Five Cultural Pillars of Perseverance" An EASY-to-read, five-page PDF. Five ideas to inspire perseverance in a growing mind.

name: Golf Coach Direct ("GCD")
reward_description: GCD founder Phil Auerbach will accompany you to the Bobby Grace Putter Studio in St. Petersburg, FL. You will be at the studio watching your putter go through the entire manufacturing process from start to finish.  It is quite amazing. Please note: any travel and hotel expenses not included.

name: Golf Coach Direct ("GCD")
reward_description: Equipment Fitting + Instruction + Playing Lessons + Golf + GCD Cap + GCD Shirt  =  Great chance for improvement and good times! 3 day, 2 night trip to St. Petersburg, FL to hang out with GCD Founder Phil Auerbach (Flight and Hotel included) + a 1 year Season Pass on GCD + GCD Cap + GCD golf shirt. You will learn all about GCD and all about your game. Phil will take you around to all of his favorite golf spots including Bobby Grace’s putter studio and the Pro Performance Golf Lab where you will pick up the best equipment that is tailored to your game. Phil will also have you learn the swing from his favorite instructors in the area, depending on who is available. Phil has your rounds of golf covered also.  He will personally have you as his guest at Feather Sound Country Club where he will take you to lunch and tell you all about Golf Coach Direct’s broader vision for the future before having you out for golf.  Phil may even have a few tips of his own around the greens for you.  He’s a true amateur but remember – Phil has taken lessons from hundreds of pros on GCD. Phil will take you to play at at least one other premiere course in the area (Course TBD depending on their availability and conditioning at the time of the trip). Hotel is Carillon Hilton located ½ mile from Feather Sound.  Further details will be arranged.  (Hotel, Florida ground transportation and flight included *Up to $400 for flight)

name: Golf Coach Direct ("GCD")
reward_description: You and two guests will join GCD Co-Founder Michael Barasch for spectacular round at Bayonne overlooking New York City plus a lot of laughs + lunch + chocolate chip cookies (you don't want to miss those). Michael will take you around for some of the most fun 18 holes of your golf career.  And then he will take you on a tour of the lighthouse which is truly magical.

name: Golf Coach Direct ("GCD")
reward_description: A trip for you and a friend to a very special top ranked private club in Tampa, FL. You and a friend will be hosted by GCD founder Phil Auerbach and one of GCD’s most trusted advisors for an incredible two days of golf and fun. You will arrive at the club in time for lunch on Day 1.   Then play golf in the afternoon, have dinner at the club, stay overnight at a luxury villa on the course, and then get up for breakfast and a morning round followed by lunch on day two.  You and your friend will also receive a seasons pass for 2016 on GCD’s new website (Up to 20 lessons). (Please note: hotel expense and Florida Ground Transportation is included, but not flight) OR A three day “Phil Tour” of 5 exclusive NYC Golf Courses with Phil and friends.  This will include three days of golf with Phil, greens fees, caddies, carts, breakfast, and lunch.  Day 1 and Day 2 will be 36 holes each on 4 different courses and Day 3 will be 18 holes at a 5th special course.   Please note: Travel and hotel expenses not included.

reward_description: *Human Core\Community Process (HCP) is a tool and workshop that promotes mind-discipline by providing exercise-routines for the mind, allowing one to better align one’s mind and one’s behaviors with one’s core. By being able to more systematically access one’s core, one is then able to make more powerful life choices. In fact, one is then able to create choices.
